## Summary
This documentation details the integration between Amplitude and TheTradeDesk, allowing advertisers to send user cohorts for targeted advertising campaigns with a 30-day TTL for users, supporting mapping to TheTradeDesk's GUID, raw device ID, or Unified ID 2.0, and requiring configuration in both platforms with advertiser credentials.

